    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm also curious about the other side of it. i hear people say that raising the wage is basically a moral necessity for workers to live with dignity, but in a small town like mine, it feels like it just puts me out of business. how do people justify those hikes when the local economy can't really support them?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
